Route to an Agent

Route work directly to the preferred agent. For example, you can route sales calls from existing customers to their account executives.

Available in: both Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience
Omni-Channel is available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Verify that you’ve completed these prerequisite tasks before you set up rules to route work directly to agents.
title: Route Work to Preferred Salesforce Agent
